    <abstract id="aspace_f0cdec59ef6b8f0fd8138b90328eccb4">The McCutcheon / Dodd, Mead mss., 1903-1944, consist of contracts and correspondence between author George Barr McCutcheon, 1866-1928, and his publisher Dodd, Mead &amp; Company.</abstract>
